ygData.title: TransFamily Couples email support list
ygData.description: This forum is an international list that offers support, discussions, and news for transgendered and CD individuals and/or their spouses or committed partners. It is one of several TransFamily lists started by Cindy and Miriam Scott in January 2000. The list is not moderated, but subscriptions must be approved by the list owner or moderator.
ygData.trailer:

You can change your subscription between digest and normal mode. You may also turn off/on email for vacation breaks.  Please contact the list owner if you need any help with this or have any questions about the list.  Thank you.
